Text: 왜 아무도 들어갈 수 없는 거야?

TextEng: Me find shield. You name be on it.
Text: 나 방패 찾았어. 너 이름 써 있어.

TextEng: I found this shield with your name on it.
You takes me 50 gold and gets you arm back.
Here, take this 50 gold and get your arm back.
Text: 여기, 금화 50개 받고 네 팔 되찾아.

TextEng: No, you keeps you gold. You needs it.
Text: 아니, 너 금 가져. 너 필요해.

TextEng: No, you keep your gold. You need it.
Text: 아니, 네 돈 가져. 네가 필요하잖아.
